{"tid":189404,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"連登有無人食過貓？","createTime":"2017-04-06T11:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T13:36:01.000Z","uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7220c1348a1e1873abe53ad5915d48d599dd59a9","tid":189404,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:45:23.000Z","msg":"過貓用涼拌的會很好吃.<br />\n<br />\n材料:美乃滋.海苔小脆片.<br />\n<br />\n調味料:香油<br />\n<br />\n烹煮時間:大約5分<br />\n<br />\n作法:把過貓切段川燙好後撈起過冰水.在用漏勺撈起把水瀝乾後<br />\n<br />\n拌點香油辦好後放置盤中大約鋪好.在把海苔片<br />\n<br />\n放上去也是鋪均勻.在把美乃滋平均擠在上面即可享用!<br />\n<br />\n小秘訣:放點芝麻也很香喔!<br />\n<br />\n我們家都是做涼拌的來吃.說真的我也很想知過貓要如何炒<br />\n<br />\n大家會點食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43637a703d3da19d16b28cc671e802d4cc092de1","tid":189404,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"無人食過貓？"},{"pid":"95ffa09530ee29aa05d58f298400991d9a52289e","tid":189404,"uid":27099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:49:09.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe7f69c9bf336ecdcf55aa8b06958808627834f","tid":189404,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:49:27.000Z","msg":"我食過熱狗"},{"pid":"e5d5bdb76340225e67a5fc764fbb1d46b2441492","tid":189404,"uid":11916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:09:16.000Z","msg":"連登有無人食過樓豬？"},{"pid":"2adface23a7cd82a4c1a95bb3e5777e99882f782","tid":189404,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:53:41.000Z","msg":"死嘅就食得多"},{"pid":"d79d409b363d850b4bfa7e06417da1a6679503f8","tid":189404,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登有無人食過樓豬？</blockquote><br />\n❓❓❓"},{